          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "ppwt002",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": { "editor": "<p>晴天娛樂城推薦網重視每位使用者的隱私權與個人資料保護。本隱私權政策旨在說明本網站如何蒐集、使用、保護及管理使用者資訊，並協助您了解相關權益與網站資料使用方式。</p><p>當您瀏覽或使用本網站服務時，即表示您已閱讀並同意本隱私權政策之內容。</p>", "text_color": "#C3CAD8", "typography_typography": "custom", "typography_font_size": { "unit": "px", "size": 17 }, "typography_line_height": { "unit": "em", "size": 1.9 } },
              "elements": []
            },
            { "id": "ppnum01", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "heading", "settings": { "title": "01", "header_size": "h6", "title_color": "#B5A8F0", "typography_typography": "custom", "typography_font_size": { "unit": "px", "size": 14 }, "typography_font_weight": "800", "typography_letter_spacing": { "unit": "px", "size": 1.2 }, "_margin": { "unit": "px", "top": "30", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": false } }, "elements": [] },
            { "id": "pph2_01", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "heading", "settings": { "title": "資料蒐集範圍", "header_size": "h2", "title_color": "#FFFFFF", "typography_typography": "custom", "typography_font_size": { "unit": "px", "size": 28 }, "typography_font_weight": "700" }, "elements": [] },
            { "id": "pptx_01", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "text-editor", "settings": { "editor": "<p>當您瀏覽本網站時，我們可能蒐集部分非個人識別資訊，以提升網站功能、改善使用體驗及分析網站流量。可能蒐集的資訊包含：</p>", "text_color": "#C3CAD8", "typography_typography": "custom", "typography_font_size": { "unit": "px", "size": 16 }, "typography_line_height": { "unit": "em", "size": 1.9 } }, "elements": [] },
            {
              "id": "ppls_01", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "icon-list",
              "settings": {
                "icon_list": [
                  { "text": "瀏覽器類型與版本", "selected_icon": { "value": "fas fa-circle", "library": "fa-solid" }, "_id": "il0101" },
                  { "text": "裝置類型", "selected_icon": { "value": "fas fa-circle", "library": "fa-solid" }, "_id": "il0102" },
                  { "text": "作業系統資訊", "selected_icon": { "value": "fas fa-circle", "library": "fa-solid" }, "_id": "il0103" },
                  { "text": "網站瀏覽紀錄", "selected_icon": { "value": "fas fa-circle", "library": "fa-solid" }, "_id": "il0104" },
                  { "text": "進入頁面與停留時間", "selected_icon": { "value": "fas fa-circle", "library": "fa-solid" }, "_id": "il0105" },
                  { "text": "點擊行為與使用習慣", "selected_icon": { "value": "fas fa-circle", "library": "fa-solid" }, "_id": "il0106" },
                  { "text": "IP 位址（依服務需求可能記錄）", "selected_icon": { "value": "fas fa-circle", "library": "fa-solid" }, "_id": "il0107" }
                ],
                "space_between": { "unit": "px", "size": 11 }, "icon_color": "#7656D7", "icon_size": { "unit": "px", "size": 8 }, "text_color": "#C3CAD8", "text_typography_typography": "custom", "text_typography_font_size": { "unit": "px", "size": 16 }
              },
              "elements": []
            },
            { "id": "pptx_01b", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "text-editor", "settings": { "editor": "<p>若未來開放會員系統、聯絡表單或活動申請功能，使用者主動提供之資訊亦可能包含<strong style=\"color:#E8ECF5\">姓名、電子郵件地址及相關聯絡資料</strong>。</p>", "text_color": "#C3CAD8", "typography_typography": "custom", "typography_font_size": { "unit": "px", "size": 16 }, "typography_line_height": { "unit": "em", "size": 1.9 } }, "elements": [] },

            { "id": "ppnum02", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "heading", "settings": { "title": "02", "header_size": "h6", "title_color": "#B5A8F0", "typography_typography": "custom", "typography_font_size": { "unit": "px", "size": 14 }, "typography_font_weight": "800", "typography_letter_spacing": { "unit": "px", "size": 1.2 }, "_margin": { "unit": "px", "top": "30", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": false } }, "elements": [] },
            { "id": "pph2_02", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "heading", "settings": { "title": "資料使用目的", "header_size": "h2", "title_color": "#FFFFFF", "typography_typography": "custom", "typography_font_size": { "unit": "px", "size": 28 }, "typography_font_weight": "700" }, "elements": [] },
            { "id": "pptx_02", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "text-editor", "settings": { "editor": "<p>本網站蒐集相關資訊主要用於以下用途：</p>", "text_color": "#C3CAD8", "typography_typography": "custom", "typography_font_size": { "unit": "px", "size": 16 }, "typography_line_height": { "unit": "em", "size": 1.9 } }, "elements": [] },
            {
